fg_segments: Our Privacy Policy How Flight Rising gathers, uses, manages, and discloses its users' data.
Information Flight Rising gathers: -IP Address -First Name -Last Name
How Flight Rising uses the above information: This information is solely used to identify and protect the account owner.
No information is sold, traded, or shared with anyone (persons or businesses).

Parties that are given access to the above information: A user's personal information is accessible by the site administration staff, with the exception being the user's password, which is irreversibly hashed per security best practices.
In the case that there is credible reason to believe an individual's life or well-being is at risk, this information may be provided to law enforcement. (01/31/2018)
Flight Rising's use of browser cookies: Our website makes use of cookies which are small digital files that are stored in your web browser that enable us to track your return visits to our website.
Your browser settings may allow you to block these cookies, but we recommend you have them enabled to help us personalize your experience.
Additionally, 3rd party advertisers on our site may use cookies for tracking purposes.
For instance, Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads and track our site traffic.
Google's use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads to visitors based on the sites they visit on the internet.
Website visitors may opt out of the DART cookie by visiting their Google ad and content network privacy policy.

raw_html:
Our Privacy Policy
How Flight Rising gathers, uses, manages, and discloses its users' data.

Information Flight Rising gathers:
-IP Address
-First Name
-Last Name
-Birthday
-E-Mail Address

How Flight Rising uses the above information:
This information is solely used to identify and protect the account owner. No information is sold, traded, or shared with anyone (persons or businesses).

Parties that are given access to the above information:
A user's personal information is accessible by the site administration staff, with the exception being the user's password, which is irreversibly hashed per security best practices. In the case that there is credible reason to believe an individual's life or well-being is at risk, this information may be provided to law enforcement. (01/31/2018)

Flight Rising's use of browser cookies:
Our website makes use of cookies which are small digital files that are stored in your web browser that enable us to track your return visits to our website. Your browser settings may allow you to block these cookies, but we recommend you have them enabled to help us personalize your experience.
Additionally, 3rd party advertisers on our site may use cookies for tracking purposes. For instance, Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads and track our site traffic. Google's use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads to visitors based on the sites they visit on the internet. Website visitors may opt out of the DART cookie by visiting their Google ad and content network privacy policy.
